<span class="obs-result-denom">/5</span>
</div>
<p class="obs-result-label">signaux identifiés</p>
<div class="obs-result-body">
<p class="obs-result-title" id="obsResultTitle"></p>
<p class="obs-result-text" id="obsResultText"></p>
